      • getSearchResultByView

        public DbSearchResult getSearchResultByView()
        Quickly return search results by using 3 views: omssaresult, mascotresult, xtandemresult. The enum 'SearchEngineView' encodes the names of the views. An FDR value of 0.2 is applied at the end to set all proteins to "visible".
        Returns:
        searchResult - returns this object search result, which is filled with data in this method
